                        </owl:unionOf>
                    </owl:Class>
                </owl:someValuesFrom>
            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>a physical examination of the soft tissue of the mouth, including the lips, mucosa, hard and soft palate, tongue, and floor of mouth</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>technically I don&apos;t need to include giniva since it is mucosa, but felt like it in the interest of avoiding questions</obo:IAO_0000116>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>Alan Ruttenberg</obo:IAO_0000119>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>http://www.dentistry.utoronto.ca/dpes/diagnostic/patients/extraoral-and-intraoral-soft-tissue-examination-patient</obo:IAO_0000119>
