        <obo:IAO_0000115>A target of material addition role that inheres in some part of a tooth and is realized in a process where dental material forms a new surface</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>Can&apos;t say the role inheres in a surface as the problem may be that the  particular surface isn&apos;t present before the restoration.</obo:IAO_0000116>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>Alan Ruttenberg</obo:IAO_0000117>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">tooth surface to be restored role</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


