            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A disorder in a tissue or organ that is marked by capillary dilatation, leukocytic infiltration, redness, heat, pain, swelling, and often loss of function, which is a response cellular injury or infection.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>ISBN:978-0-8153-4505-3</obo:IAO_0000119>
